imports "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureMap/Element4to5"

group base64Binary(source src : base64BinaryR4, target tgt : base64BinaryR5) extends Element <<type+>> {
  src.value as v -> tgt.value = v "base64BinaryValue";
}

}
